mpson-min.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="铁娘子表演的布鲁斯·狄金森（Bruce Dickinson）。信用 - 戴夫·辛普森（Dave Simpson）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden-performing.-Credit-Dave-Simpson-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden-performing.-Credit-Dave-Simpson-min-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden-performing.-Credit-Dave-Simpson-min-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden-performing.-Credit-Dave-Simpson-min-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden-performing.-Credit-Dave-Simpson-min-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Bruce-Dickinson-of-Iron-Maiden-performing.-Credit-Dave-Simpson-min-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iron-maiden">Iron Maiden</a>正在发行一本名为<em>“无限梦”</em>的新视觉书，记载了乐队50年的职业生涯。</p><p>预计将在2025年秋季登陆，这本精装本将包含标志性专辑和单一艺术品的图像，乐队的过去和现在乐器，舞台道具，手写的歌词和档案手工艺品。还将拍摄乐队的照片，包括一些以前看不见的照片。</p><p>即将上映的《铁娘子》一书将包含贝斯手史蒂夫·哈里斯（Steve Harris）的前言，主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-dickinson">布鲁斯·迪金森（Bruce Dickinson）</a>的后记。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.kerrang.com/iron-maiden-to-release-astonishing-visual-book-celebrating-50-years-of-the-band" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>克朗说：</em></a> “我为这本书发掘的一些东西感到惊喜。” 。 “我知道我从早期开始就保留了很多事情，但是它们持续了很好，摄影使他们重新栩栩如生。我希望粉丝们会喜欢看这样的所有东西！现在是将所有这些都聚集在一起的合适时机。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHBYQVGClWn/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; pa